frontmatter.description: Obsidian supports right-to-left (RTL) languages such as Arabic, Dhivehi, Hebrew, Farsi, Syriac, and Urdu. These languages are spoken by more than 600 million people. When developing plugins and themes for Obsidian it is important consider how your interface changes will adapt to the direction of the language interface and content.
